#: ../../source/official-mirror.rst:5
msgid ""
"Official Debian archive mirrors get an address of the form ftp.country "
"code.debian.org. These are the best advertised and most used sites; the "
"face of Debian for most people."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/official-mirror.rst:10
msgid ""
"<toc-add-entry name=\"list\">List of official Debian archive mirrors"
"</toc-add-entry>"
msgstr ""

